                                src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1383184766959120385/MM9DHPWC_400x400.jpg"
                                alt=""><a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk">Elon Musk</a></td>
                        <td><a class="waves-effect waves-light blue lighten-2 btn" href="">Follow</a></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><img class="followAvatar"
                                src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1343584679664873479/Xos3xQfk_400x400.jpg"
                                alt=""><a href="https://twitter.com/Google">Google</a></td>
                        <td><a class="waves-effect waves-light blue lighten-2 btn" href="">Follow</a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><img class="followAvatar"
                                src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1318271172216324097/O7Xaryg2_400x400.jpg"
